. Recommended to [download the wheel](https://oracle.sharepoint.com/sites/ai-for-employees/Shared%20Documents/Forms/AllItems.aspx?id=%2Fsites%2Fai%2Dfor%2Demployees%2FShared%20Documents%2FAI%20for%20Engineers%2FPlugin%20Downloads%2FAider%20%2D%20CLI&viewid=523d1542%2D44f5%2D4efc%2Db685%2D82d6467c3829&csf=1&web=1&e=aPt5Ra&CID=a337f41e%2D2adf%2D417c%2Da95f%2D42ea326c554f&FolderCTID=0x01200008E7535C0D00CD448E4A8499AAC8B8AE) and install it with `pip`:\n\n[221 more lines in file. Use offset=41 to continue.]"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777299676633}}
